OL,3,CLondon jumps into top 10 in global
OL,4,C'most expensive cities' list
OL,6,FLondon has jumped into the top 10 list
OL,7,Fin a global index which looks at the
OL,8,Fmost expensive cities for expatriate
OL,9,Femployees.
OL,11,FThe city has moved up nine places
OL,12,Fsince last year, to be ranked eighth
OL,13,Fin Mercer's 2024 cost-of-living city
OL,14,Franking.
OL,16,FPlaced just below New York on the
OL,17,Flist, London jumped up the list thanks
OL,18,Fto factors including the general cost
OL,19,Fof living and rental prices, according
OL,20,Fto those behind the list.
