OL,3,CLondon jumps into top 10 in global
OL,4,C'most expensive cities' list
OL,6,FHong Kong retained the top spot in
OL,7,Fthis year's ranking, followed by
OL,8,FSingapore. Swiss cities Zurich, Geneva
OL,9,Fand Basel round out the top five most
OL,10,Fexpensive cities.
OL,12,FEdinburgh was placed at 53, Glasgow at
OL,13,F68, Birmingham at 78, Aberdeen at 82,
OL,14,Fand Belfast at 87.
OL,16,FParis was ranked 29th and Dublin at 41.
