OL,3,CLondon jumps into top 10 in global
OL,4,C'most expensive cities' list
OL,6,FRising housing costs in many cities
OL,7,Faround the world have been a challenge
OL,8,Ffor employers, with volatile inflation
OL,9,Ftrends also putting a strain on
OL,10,Fworkers' compensation packages, Mercer
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThese factors can make it difficult
OL,14,Ffor employers to attract and retain
OL,15,Ftop talent and can increase
OL,16,Fcompensation and benefits expenses,
OL,17,Flimit talent mobility and raise
OL,18,Foperational costs, the report added.
