OL,3,CLondon jumps into top 10 in global
OL,4,C'most expensive cities' list
OL,6,FYvonne Traber, Mercer's global
OL,7,Fmobility leader, said: "Cost-of-living
OL,8,Fchallenges have had a significant
OL,9,Fimpact on multinational organisations
OL,10,Fand their employees.
OL,12,F"It's important for organisations to
OL,13,Fstay informed about cost-of-living
OL,14,Ftrends and inflation rates and seek
OL,15,Finput from employees on these issues
OL,16,Fto effectively manage their effects.
OL,18,F"High living costs may cause assignees
OL,19,Fto adjust their lifestyle, cut back on
OL,20,Fdiscretionary spending or even
OL,21,Fstruggle to meet their basic needs."
